'''拉蒙塔涅兄弟'''（{{lang-en|'''The LaMontages brothers'''}}）是由雷奈（Rene）、蒙泰居（Montaigu）、威廉（William）和摩根（Morgan）組成的[[上流社會|上流社會]][[走私酒類|私酒販們]]<ref name="Anti-SaloonLeague">{{cite book |last=Cherrington |first=Ernest Hurst |date=1924 |title=The Anti-saloon League Year Book: An Encyclopedia of Facts and Figures Dealing with the Liquor Traffic and the Temperance Reform |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Ao_gKWXvb3gC&q=The+LaMontages+brothers+Prohibition+bootleg&dq=The+LaMontages+brothers+Prohibition+bootleg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CB0Q6AEwAGoVChMIhcam8KaCyAIVi1ySCh1IswQG |publisher=Anti-Saloon League |page=157 |language=en |access-date=2021-02-12 |archive-date=2016-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160429214236/https://books.google.com/books?id=Ao_gKWXvb3gC&q=The+LaMontages+brothers+Prohibition+bootleg&dq=The+LaMontages+brothers+Prohibition+bootleg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CB0Q6AEwAGoVChMIhcam8KaCyAIVi1ySCh1IswQG |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="RepealReview">{{cite book |date=1959 |title=Repeal Review |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UlQiAQAAIAAJ&q=The+LaMontages+brothers+Prohibition+bootleg&dq=The+LaMontages+brothers+Prohibition+bootleg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CCEQ6AEwAWoVChMIhcam8KaCyAIVi1ySCh1IswQG |publisher=Repeal Associates |page=87 |language=en |access-date=2021-02-12 |archive-date=2016-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160425001107/https://books.google.com/books?id=UlQiAQAAIAAJ&q=The+LaMontages+brothers+Prohibition+bootleg&dq=The+LaMontages+brothers+Prohibition+bootleg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CCEQ6AEwAWoVChMIhcam8KaCyAIVi1ySCh1IswQG |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://archive.org/details/wreckingoftheeig006616mbp |title = THE WRECKING OF THE EIGHTEENTH AMENDMENT |author = Ernest Gordon |publisher = Internet Archive |language = en}}</ref>，他們在[[美國禁酒令|美國禁酒令]]早期透過非法生意每年賺取2,000,000美元。

其中一個不滿的成員提供了線索導致他們被捕和被定罪，但美國助理司法部長Mabel Willibrand報告說，「所有可想到的政治和個人起訴，包括一位[[內閣|內閣]]官員的起訴，都被壓制了。」1923年2月9日，聯邦法院對每個兄弟罰款2,000美元，並判處其中3人入獄4個月，以及1人入獄2個月。<ref name="Anti-SaloonLeague"/><ref name="RepealReview"/>然而，他們在《{{link-en|社會名人錄|Social Register}}》上的名單於1929年才被撤銷。

